name: Main Theorem of QTKE-groups
prop: The finite nonabelian simple QTKE-groups consist of the following:
(1) Groups of Lie type of characteristic 2 and Lie rank at most 2, but U(5,q) only for q = 4.
(2) PSL(2,p) for Mersenne primes and Fermat primes.
(3) The groups Alt5, Alt6, Alt8, Alt9, M11, M12, M22, M23, M24, HS, He, Ru, J2, J3, and J4.
(4) The groups PSL(4,2), PSL(5,2), Sp(6,2), G(2,3), Lep(3,3), and Lep(4,3).
